%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk%20wants%20xAI%20to%20build%20the%20world's%20most%20powerful%20supercomputer%20using%20Nvidia%20chips%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226304%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Elon%20Musk%20next%20to%20xAI's%20logo%20on%20a%20phone%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66559d9120abc1efe8fdde8b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224203%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EElon%20Musk's%20xAI%20has%20raised%20a%20further%20%246%20billion.%3Cp%3EAnadolu%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EElon%20Musk%20is%20building%20a%20supercomputer%20that%20he%20wants%20running%20by%20fall%202025%2C%20The%20Information%20reported.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%C2%A0%26quot%3Bgigafactory%20of%20compute%26quot%3B%20will%20use%20Nvidia%20GPUs%20and%20aims%20to%20surpass%20Meta's%20big%20cluster%20of%20chips.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ExAI%20has%20raised%20another%20%246%20billion%20and%20Musk%20invested%20%24750%20million%2C%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20big%20AI%20ambitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20billionaire%20wants%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Df3b721f433ce8574f269a78dc9b73f4ae6be44c07605e66c236f3f943930e5b9%26postID%3D665598914d89916b4e3fc0d4%26postSlug%3Delon-musk-xai-build-powerful-supercomputer-nvidia-chips-oracle-servers-2024-5%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.theinformation.com%252Farticles%252Fmusk-plans-xai-supercomputer-dubbed-gigafactory-of-compute%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuild%20a%20supercomputer%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20have%20it%20running%20by%20fall%202025%2C%20The%20Information%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ExAI%20announced%20Sunday%20that%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-xai-raised-6-billion-funding-vc-saudi-