%20the%20company%20cofounded%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-larry-ellison-team-up-ai-farming-tool-starlink-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMusk's%20friend%20Larry%20Ellison%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20build%20the%20supercomputer%20and%20splash%20out%20%2410%20billion%20to%20rent%20its%20cloud%20servers%20in%20the%20coming%20years%2C%20The%20Information%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20xAI%20chief's%20goals%20are%20ambitious%20given%20the%20%24100%20billion%20Stargate%20supercomputer%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-openai-plan-100-billion-supercomputer-stargate-artificial-intelligence-report-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMicrosoft%20and%20OpenAI%20are%20building%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20not%20expected%20to%20start%20operating%20until%202028.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ExAI%20is%20hiring%20for%20several%20roles%20in%20San%20Francisco%20and%20London%20as%20it%20seeks%20to%20expand%20and%20catch%20up%20with%20its%20rivals.%20Musk%20wrote%20on%20X%20on%20Monday%3A%20%26quot%3BJoin%20xAI%20if%20you%20believe%20in%20our%20mission%20of%20understanding%20the%20universe%2C%20which%20requires%20maximally%20rigorous%20pursuit%20of%20the%20truth%2C%20without%20regard%20to%20popularity%20or%20political%20correctness.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ExAI%20didn't%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider%2C%20made%20outside%20normal%20working%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-xai-build-powerful-supercomputer-nvidia-chips-oracle-servers-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716889917000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66559dd7a961b37edf3a2fc8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-xai-build-powerful-supercomputer-nvidia-chips-oracle-servers-2024-5%2