ttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-bankman-fried-sentenced-prison-ftx-alameda-research-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewho%20is%20currently%20in%20prison%3C%2Fa%3E)%20or%20Binance's%20CZ%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fformer-binance-ceo-sentenced-to-four-months-in-prison-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewho%20is%20headed%20to%20prison%3C%2Fa%3E).%20Unlike%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fsec-sues-coinbase-violating-securities-regulation-binance-crypto-regulation-gensler-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECoinbase%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20regulators%20don't%20seem%20to%20be%20sniffing%20around.%20Sure%2C%20the%20company%20has%20high-profile%20marketing%20efforts%2C%20but%20day%20to%20day%2C%20Crypto.com%20doesn't%20really%20come%20up%20much%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECrypto.com%20is%20one%20of%20those%20things%20I've%20long%20placed%20in%20my%20%26quot%3BI%20wonder%20what%20the%20deal%20is%26quot%3B%20column%2C%20along%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjojo-siwa-rebrand-shows-difficulty-child-stars-grow-up-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJojo%20Siwa%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbird-flu-virus-chickens-cows-human-food-outbreaks-pandemic-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebird%20flu%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ff1-nascar-races-motorsports-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20difference%20between%20F1%20and%20NASCAR%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20seems%20impossible%20to%20watch%20a%20sporting%20event%20without%20seeing%20its%20name%20somewhere%2C%20and%20yet%20I%20rarely%20chat%20with%20someone%20who%20uses%20it%20or%20come%20across%20its%20name%20in%20headlines.%20Part%20of%20the%20issue%20is%20that%20I%20live%20in%20New%20York%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhelp.crypto.com%2Fen%2Farticles%2F1341655-which-are-the-available-markets%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhere%20its%20services%20aren't%20allowed%3C%2Fa%3E.%20(That's%20not%20a%20knock%20on%20the%20company%20%E2%80%94%20for%20a%20lot%20of%20crypto%20exchanges%2C%20the%20Empire%20State%20is%20a%20tough%20nut%20to%20crack.)%20But%20it's%20also%20a%20rather%20nebulous%20entity%20in%20the%20American%20market.%20It%20says%20it's%20got%20100%20million%20users%20globally%2C%20but%20it%20still%20seems%20to%20fly%20a%20little%20under%20the%20radar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOften%2C%20when%20I%20mention%20Crypto.com%20to%20someone%20who%20works%20in%20the%20crypto%20industry%2C%20they%20tell%20me%20they%20know%20about%20it%2C%20of%20course.%20When%20I%20ask%20exactly%20what%20they%20know%20about%20it%2C%20they%20come%20up%20pretty%20empty.%20Maybe%20it's%20mainly%20popular%20abroad%2C%20they%20speculate%2C%20or%20only%20for%20novices.%20Google%20data%20indicates%20that%20while%20a%20good%20chunk%20of%20the%20search%20interest%20does%20come%20from%20America%2C%20more%20comes%20from%20outside%20the%20US%2C%20notably%20from%20Singapore%2C%20Nigeria%2C%20and%20Bulgaria.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHuh%2C%20I%20guess%20bigger%20than%20I%20thought%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20crypto%20evangelist%20remarked%20after%20looking%20up%20its%20trading%20volume.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20own%20the%20Lakers'%20arena%3F%20I've%20always%20been%20so%20confused%20on%20how%20they%20did%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20crypto%20entrepreneur%20said.%20(To%20be%20fair%2C%20the%20company%20doesn't%20own%20the%20arena%3B%20it%20just%20bought%20the%20naming%20rights.)%20He'd%20set%20up%20a%20Crypto.com%20account%20during%20the%202021-2022%20market%20cycle%20to%20do%20a%20specific%20maneuver%20not%20allowed%20on%20Coinbase%20at%20the%20time%2C%20but%20he%20hasn't%20really%20used%20it%20since%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20asked%20Nic%20Carter%2C%20a%20general%20partner%20at%20Castle%20Island%20Ventures%2C%20about%20the%20company%2C%20he%20replied%20in%20an%20email%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20kind%20of%20a%20mystery%2C%20yes.%26quot%3BHe%20added%20that%2C%20like%20me%2C%20he%20doesn't%20know%20anyone%20who%20uses%20it.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20think%20that%20reflects%20the%20user%20base%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20not%20necessarily%20crypto-natives%20but%20rather%20retail%20that%20wants%20a%20casual%20and%20accessible%20experience%20(is%20my%20understanding)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECrypto.com%20is%20positioning%20itself%20as%20the%20new%20face%20of%20crypto%2C%20even%20as%20it%20remains%20rather%20faceless%20itself.%20It%20might%20prove%20to%20be%20a%20smart%20move%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20boosting%20its%20brand%20and%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20its%20consumer%20base%20while%20avoiding%20much%20of%20the%20scrutiny%20other%20exchanges%20have%20faced.%20For%20the%20time%20being%2C%20Crypto.com%20is%20balancing%20between%20notability%20and%20infamy.%20It's%20walking%20softly%20but%20carrying%20a%20big%20ad%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Crypto.com%20only%20really%20burst%20onto%20the%20American%20scene%20over%20the%20past%20four%20years%20or%20so%2C%20it's%20been%20around%20for%20a%20while.%20Originally%20named%20Monaco%2C%20the%20exchange%20was%20founded%20in%202016%20in%20Hong%20Kong%20by%20Kris%20Marszalek%2C%20a%20Polish-born%20entrepreneur%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2022%2F12%2F09%2Fcryptocom-kris-marszalek-involved-bankruptcy-offshore-holdings-client-money-monaco.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewith%20a%20colorful%20past%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20a%20handful%20of%20others.%20Amid%20the%202017%20crypto%20run%2C%20it%20raised%20money%20from%20the%20public%20via%20an%20initial%20coin%20offering%20%E2%80%94%20creating%20and%20selling%20a%20digital%20token%20of%20its%20own%2C%20similar%20to%20a%20stock-market%20IPO.%20In%202018%2C%20the%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2018%2F7%2F6%2F17540818%2Fcrypto-com-domain-matt-blaze-monaco-mco-cryptology-sale%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elanded%20the%20coveted%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FCrypto.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECrypto.com%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2018%2F7%2F6%2F17540818%2Fcrypto-com-domain-matt-blaze-monaco-mco-cryptology-sale%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20domain%20name%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20purchasing%20it%20for%20an%20undisclosed%20amount%20from%20an%20academic%20who%20had%20long%20refused%20to%20sell%20it.%20(Even%20more%20confusingly%2C%20Crypto.com%20is%20technically%20operated%20by%20Foris%20DAX%20Asia%2C%20which%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2FCrypto_com%2Fcomments%2Fsfl1v4%2Fcdc_and_foris_dax_inc_online_1099k%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Escan%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2FCrypto_com%2Fcomments%2Ftlwxpu%2Fi_just_had_20_deducted_from_my_checking_from%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReddit%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20can%20befuddle%20many%20users%20when%20their%20tax%20paperwork%20comes%20in.%20It's%20also%20the%20name%20Crypto.com%20lobbies%20under.)%20Crypto.com's%20primary%20business%20is%20its%20cryptocurrency%20exchange%2C%20which%20works%20as%20a%20middleman%20for%20people%20buying%20and%20selling%20crypto%2C%20but%20it%20also%20offers%20other%20products%2C%20including%20crypto%20Visa%20cards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%202021-22%20market%20cycle%20is%20when%20Crypto.com%2C%20now%20headquartered%20in%20Singapore%2C%20made%20its%20big%20splash.%20In%20late%202021%2C%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstaples-center-la-being-renamed-crypto-com-arena-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebought%20the%20naming%20rights%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20what%20was%20then%20the%20Staples%20Center%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20as%20part%20of%20a%2020-year%2C%20%24700%20million%20deal.%20It%20signed%20sponsorship%20deals%20with%20UFC%20and%20F1%20while%20also%20rolling%20its%20%26quot%3Bfortune%20favors%20the%20brave%26quot%3B%20ad%20campaign%2C%20which%20originally%20featured%20Matt%20Damon.%20Crypto.com%20was%20seeking%20brand%20awareness%2C%20and%20it%20was%20willing%20to%20spend%20millions%20upon%20millions%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20one%20brick%20in%20a%20bigger%20wall%20of%20introducing%20Crypto.com%20as%20a%20brand%20to%20the%20world%20and%20communicating%20what%20our%20core%20values%20are%2C%26quot%3B%20Steven%20Kalifowitz%2C%20Crypto.com's%20chief%20marketing%20officer%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcryptocom-how-startup-bought-staples-center-rights-700-million-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20moment%2C%20it%20all%20sort%20of%20made%20sense.%20FTX%20was%20flying%20high%20and%20had%20paid%20%24135%20million%20to%20slap%20its%20name%20on%20the%20Miami%20Heat's%20stadium.%20Its%20founder%2C%20SBF%2C%20was%20running%20around%20with%20Bill%20Clinton%20and%20Tony%20Blair%20in%20the%20Bahamas%20and%20suggesting%20he'd%20spend%20%241%20billion%20on%20the%202024%20election.%20Binance's%20CZ%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fbinance-ceo-chaopeng-zhang-cz-forbes-investment-crypto-adoption-media-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etalking%20about%20investing%20%24200%20million%20in%20Forbes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20saying%20it%20would%20push%20media%20companies%20toward%20adopting%20crypto%20and%20lead%20to%20the%20decentralization%20of%20the%20industry.%20But%20we%20know%20how%20the%20story%20ends%3A%20FTX%20imploded%2C%20along%20with%20some%20other%20high-profile%20crypto%20projects%2C%20and%20crypto%20winter%20set%20in.%20A%20lot%20of%20crypto's%20mini-emperors%20turned%20out%20to%20have%20no%20clothes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECrypto.com%2C%20however%2C%20managed%20to%20weather%20the%20storm%2C%20though%20not%20perfectly.%20The%20company%20accidentally%20sent%20some%20%24400%20million%20to%20the%20wrong%20account%20in%20November%202022%2C%20prompting%20some%20users%20to%20pull%20their%20money%20out%20of%20the%20platform.%20At%20the%20start%20of%202023%2C%20it%20laid%20off%2020%25%20of%20its%20workforce%2C%20blaming%20economic%20headwinds%20and%20FTX's%20collapse.%20The%20Financial%20Times%20reported%20last%20June%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FCrypto.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECrypto.com%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2Fb5d2bf4b-225c-4f30-9f1c-cbe8dc762fa8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20was%20operating%20internal%20proprietary%20trading%20teams%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20US%20regulators%20had%20dinged%20Binance%20for%2C%20even%20though%20Crypto.com%20insisted%20it%20was%20fine.%20The%20regulatory%20environment%20in%20the%20US%20appears%20to%20have%20made%20the%20company%20a%20little%20nervous%20%E2%80%94%20it%20shut%20down%20its%20American%20institutional%20exchange%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20US%2C%20Crypto.com%20has%20managed%20to%20avoid%20much%20of%20the%20blowback%20its%20competitors%20have%20faced.%20(This%20isn't%20the%20case%20in%20other%20countries%20%E2%80%94%20in%20the%20Netherlands%2C%20for%20example%2C%20it%20was%20fined%20for%20operating%20without%20registration.)%20While%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission%20has%20gone%20after%20Coinbase%20and%20Kraken%20for%20operating%20unregistered%20securities%20exchanges%2C%20it%20hasn't%20made%20a%20peep%20about%20Crypto.com.%20Crypto.com%20has%20so%20far%20ducked%20notice%2C%20even%20though%20it's%20running%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20same%20playbook.%20In%20April%2C%20the%20company's%20chief%20operating%20officer%20acknowledged%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdecrypt.co%2F226137%2Fcrypto-sponsorships-sec-scrutiny-worth-trade-off%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20interview%20with%20Decrypt%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20its%20big-budget%20marketing%20efforts%20could%20put%20a%20target%20on%20its%20back%20but%20said%20the%20trade-off%20was%20worth%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECrypto.com's%20determination%20to%20push%20ahead%2C%20both%20loudly%20and%20quietly%2C%20has%20set%20it%20up%20to%20try%20to%20capitalize%20on%20the%20market's%20recent%20run.%20Bitcoin%20is%20once%20again%20on%20the%20up%20and%20up%2C%20and%20so%20too%20is%20Crypto.com.%20The%20company%20is%20hiring%20again%2C%20it's%20advertising%20aggressively%20again%2C%20and%20it's%20talking%20a%20big%20game%20about%20its%20business%20prospects%20%E2%80%94%20its%20CEO%2C%20Marszalek%2C%20told%20Bloomberg%20in%20April%20that%20it%20was%20looking%20to%20triple%20its%20number%20of%20registered%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EData%20from%20the%20marketing-intelligence%20firm%20Sensor%20Tower%20indicates%20crypto%20advertisers'%20digital%20spending%20in%20the%20US%20increased%20by%20185%25%20year%20over%20year%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%202024.%20Crypto.com%20spent%20eight%20times%20as%20much%20as%20Coinbase%20on%20digital%20advertising%20during%20that%20period.%20(It's%20worth%20noting%20that%20back%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%202022%2C%20Crypto.com%20actually%20outspent%20FTX%20on%20digital%20ads%20by%20a%20bit.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20thing%20about%20all%20Crypto.com's%20advertising%20dollars%20is%20that%20they%20seem%20to%20be%20only%20effective-ish.%20Data%20compiled%20by%20CCData%20shows%20that%20Crypto.com%20has%20a%202.3%25%20market%20share%20by%20trading%20volumes%20on%20the%20spot%20market%20globally%2C%20which%20is%20about%20half%20of%20Coinbase%2C%20which%20has%204%25%2C%20and%20only%20slightly%20above%20Kraken%2C%20which%20has%201.4%25.%20(Globally%2C%20Binance%20is%20still%20dominant.)%20According%20to%20Sensor%20Tower%2C%20Crypto.com%20saw%20a%20140%25%20increase%20in%20downloads%20in%20March%20from%20the%20prior%20month%2C%20though%20it%20fell%20slightly%20behind%20Coinbase%2C%20which%20had%20a%20160%25%20increase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECrypto.com%20didn't%20respond%20to%20multiple%20requests%20for%20interviews%20or%20comments%20for%20this%20story.%20Most%20of%20the%20people%20I%20did%20speak%20to%20gave%20the%20verbal%20equivalent%20of%20a%20shrug%20when%20I%20asked%20what%20they%20thought%20of%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20crypto%20executive%20said%20part%20of%20the%20issue%20was%20that%20Crypto.com%2C%20being%20an%20upstart%20from%20Asia%2C%20is%20a%20little%20outside%20Silicon%20Valley's%20mainstream%20crypto%20circles.%20Similar%20to%20the%20clubby%20%26quot%3BPayPal%20Mafia%26quot%3B%20that%20dominated%20software%20in%20the%202010s%2C%20a%20sort%20of%20Coinbase%20crew%20has%20its%20hold%20on%20the%20crypto%20industry%20of%20the%202020s.%20The%20exec%20wasn't%20too%20keen%20on%20Crypto.com's%20flashy%20advertising%20either%2C%20describing%20it%20as%20%26quot%3Bdecadent%26quot%3B%20and%20irresponsible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20that%20buying%20of%20stadiums%20and%20renaming%20stuff%2C%20it's%20just%20kind%20of%20viewed%20as%20lame%20by%20most%20people%20in%20crypto%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20tackiest%20thing%20and%20frankly%20irresponsible%20thing%20to%20do%20is%20to%20roll%20out%20FOMO%20ads.%20'Buy%20crypto%20or%20get%20left%20behind'%20is%20a%20really%20irresponsible%20message.%20JPMorgan%20doesn't%20do%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20despite%20the%20company's%20ability%20to%20dodge%20serious%20regulatory%20scrutiny%2C%20it%20hasn't%20engendered%20a%20lot%20of%20goodwill%20among%20some%20crypto%20evangelists.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20supportive%20of%20bitcoin%2C%20but%20I%20think%20Crypto.com%20is%20overall%20a%20big%20negative%20for%20the%20American%20public.%20It's%20very%20confusing.%20It's%20a%20casino%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Alex%20Gladstein%2C%20who%20as%20the%20chief%20strategy%20officer%20at%20the%20Human%20Rights%20Foundation%20has%20argued%20that%20bitcoin%20is%20important%20for%20advancing%20human%20rights%20and%20freedom.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20go%20to%20the%20website%2C%20they%20encourage%20you%20to%20try%20and%20bet%20on%20these%20coins%20that%20go%20to%20zero.%20I%20don't%20think%20it's%20anything%20to%20do%20with%20financial%20empowerment%20for%20people%20or%20any%20sort%20of%20alternative%20wealth%20building.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgambling-young-men-sports-betting-crypto-meme-stock-market-addiction-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20casino%20thing%20could%20be%20said%20about%20most%20crypto%20exchanges%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20and%20sports-betting%20apps%2C%20and%20many%20regular%20trading%20apps.%20Crypto.com%20seems%20to%20be%20careful%20about%20coloring%20within%20the%20regulatory%20lines.%20The%20head%20of%20its%20legal%20department%20in%20the%20Americas%20just%20put%20out%20a%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D6f2f6690546fff16a8fb41dc872dd0598a2be0e31a3a70bc9c7d091e5572e5e0%26postID%3D664e3df018e7b72f111925f6%26postSlug%3Dcrypto-com-commercial-eminem-matt-damon-coinbase-bitcoin-arena-2024-5%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FCrypto-Legal-Handbook-Guide-Decentralized%252Fdp%252FB0D221XT83%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecrypto%20legal%20handbook%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20which%2C%20OK.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECrypto.com%20is%20embedded%20in%20our%20culture%2C%20and%20it%20isn't.%20It's%20sort%20of%20taken%20on%20the%20FTX%20mantle%20but%20with%20a%20more%20anonymous%20bent.%20For%20the%20company%2C%20it's%20a%20pretty%20savvy%20space%20in%20which%20to%20operate%3A%20ubiquitous%20but%20relatively%20anonymous.%20For%20everyone%20else%2C%20mileage%20may%20vary%20on%20how%20you%20feel%20about%20the%20whole%20thing.%20It's%20a%20good%20reminder%20that%2C%20whatever%20the%20company%2C%20it's%20better%20to%20use%20exchanges%20only%20for%20trading%20your%20crypto%20assets%2C%20not%20for%20storing%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaybe%20Eminem%20won't%20come%20to%20regret%20voicing%20those%20ads%20like%20Matt%20Damon%20did.%20Or%20maybe%20in%20five%20years%20we'll%20be%20looking%20back%20at%20this%20moment%20and%20saying%3A%20%26quot%3BRemember%20that%20one%20crypto%20company%3F%20Is%20it%20still%20where%20the%20Lakers%20play%3F%20Or%20is%20it%20now%20something%20else%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Femily-stewart%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EEmily%20Stewart%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20correspondent%20at%20Business%20Insider%2C%20writing%20about%20business%20and%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcrypto-com-commercial-eminem-matt-damon-coinbase-bitcoin-arena-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716889621000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664f547e20abc1efe8fcd5a0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcrypto-com-commercial-eminem-matt-damon-coinbase-bitcoin-arena-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Crypto.com%20is%20everywhere%3A%20the%20Lakers%20arena%2C%20Formula%201%2C%20UFC%20fights%2C%20commercials%20with%20Matt%20Damon%20and%20Eminem.%20But%20no%20one%20actually%20knows%20much%20about%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22estewart%40insider.com%20(Emily%20Stewart)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcrypto-com-commercial-eminem-matt-damon-coinbase-bitcoin-arena-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian%20climber%20dies%20following%20Everest%20bid%2C%20eighth%20death%20this%20season%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716889201000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110495141%2Cimgsize-713408.cms%22