%20police%20are%20examining%20CCTV%20footage%20from%20the%20campus%20to%20identify%20the%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBihar%20minister%20Ashok%20Choudhary%20has%20posted%20a%20photo%20of%20himself%20and%20Harsh%20and%20said%20no%20amount%20of%20criticism%20of%20the%20attack%20is%20enough.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20authorities%20regarding%20this%20incident.%20Those%20guilty%20will%20be%20arrested%20soon%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20JDU%20leader%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20government%20is%20with%20the%20family%20in%20this%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20has%20slammed%20the%20Nitish%20Kumar-led%20BJP-JDU%20government%20over%20the%20incident.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20very%20unfortunate.%20The%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20is%20worsening%20by%20the%20day%20ever%20since%20the%20NDA%20government%20was%20formed.%20They%20have%20no%20control%20on%20the%20administration.%20The%20guilty%20must%20be%20arrested%20at%20the%20earliest%20and%20face%20strict%20punishment%2C%26quot%3B%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%2C%20RJD's%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETargeting%20the%20BJP%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20this%20had%20happened%20in%20our%20term%2C%20they%20would%20have%20hit%20the%20streets%20and%20shouted%20'jungleraj'.%20Where%20are%20they%20now%3F%20What%20are%20they%20doing%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716887880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F0ca7a7hg_harsh-raj_625x300_28_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fharsh-raj-masked-men-with-sticks-beat-student-22-to-death-on-patna-college-campus-5762827%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%2022-year-old%20student%20was%20beaten%20to%20death%20on%20the%20campus%20of%20a%20law%20college%20in%20Bihar's%20capital%2C%20Patna.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fharsh-raj-masked-men-with-sticks-beat-student-22-to-death-on-patna-college-campus-5762827%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fharsh-raj-masked-men-with-sticks-beat-student-22-to-death-on-patna-college-campus-5762827%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fharsh-raj-masked-men-with-sticks-beat-student-22-to-death-on-patna-college-campus-5762827%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22New%20Viral%20Rage%20Ritual%20Trend%20Has%20Women%20Screaming%2C%20Smashing%20Sticks%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20world%20increasingly%20fraught%20with%20stress%2C%20anxiety%20and%20frustration%2C%20many%20people%20are%20searching%20for%20ways%20to%20manage%20their%20emotions.%20One%20such%20method%20gaining%20attention%20on%20the%20internet%20is%20%26quot%3Brage%20ritual%26quot%3B%2C%20in%20which%20women%20are%20paying%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20in%20the%20United%20States%20to%20participate%20in%20screaming%20ceremonies%20and%20breaking%20objects.%20The%20ritual%20is%20meant%20to%20effectively%20release%20pent-up%20anger.%20The%20ceremony%20is%20usually%20held%20in%20forests%20where%20women%20unleash%20lungfuls%20of%20deafening%20shrieks%20and%20use%20sticks%20to%20beat%20objects%20on%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParticipants%20are%20encouraged%20to%20think%20of%20people%20and%20experiences%20that%20have%20wronged%20them%20and%20to%20scream%20and%20swing%20the%20sticks%20for%20at%20least%2020%20minutes%2C%20or%20until%20they%20can%20no%20longer%20move%20their%20arms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20like%2C%20'Don't%20be%20a%20bitch'%20or%20'Don't%20be%20angry'%20or%20'Don't%20be%20aggressive'%20or%20'Don't%20stand%20up%20for%20yourself%2C'%20'Don't%20protect%20your%20integrity%2C'%20'Don't%20tell%20anyone%20that%20they%20don't%20have%20consent%20to%20touch%20your%20body%20or%20speak%20to%20you%20in%20a%20certain%20way.'%20There%20are%20particular%20emotions%20that%20are%20accepted%20in%20the%20gender%20binary%20that%20we%20each%20need%20to%20feel.%20Men%20need%20to%20cry%20-%20and%20it's%20so%20healthy%20for%20men%20to%20cry%20-%20and%20women%20need%20to%20be%20able%20to%20get%20angry%2C%26quot%3B%20Mia%20Banducci%2C%20who%20holds%20such%20rituals%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usatoday.com%2Fstory%2Flife%2Fhealth-wellness%2F2024%2F05%2F08%2Frage-rituals-women-screaming-woods-why%2F73595511007%2F%5C%22%3Etold%20%3Cem%3EUSA%20Today%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20has%20held%20many%20such%20ceremonies%2C%20which%20have%20evolved%20from%20small%20events%20for%20friends%20to%20overnight%20retreats.%20One%20such%20endeavour%20ranges%20from%20%242%2C000%20to%20%244%2C000%20in%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20shorter%20one-day%20version%20too%20that%20costs%20%24222%20per%20ticket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKimberly%20Helmus%2C%20one%20of%20the%20participants%2C%20revealed%20what%20she%20feels%20about%20the%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20place%20where%20you%20can%20see%20women%20be%20able%20to%20be%20angry%20like%20that%20and%20it%20not%20be%20condemned%3A%20'She's%20just%20hormonal.%20She's%20just%20unhinged.%20She's%20just%20crazy.%20She's%20just%20on%20her%20period.%20She's%20just%2C%20whatever.'%20This%20was%20a%20place%20where%20you%20were%2C%20probably%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20a%20really%2C%20really%20long%20time%2C%20if%20ever%2C%20able%20to%20scream%20out%20loud%20things%20about%20how%20you%20felt%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Helmus%20told%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20took%20part%20in%20a%20rage%20ritual%20two%20and%20a%20half%20years%20after%20her%20divorce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20ceremonies%20have%20gone%20viral%20on%20TikTok%2C%20where%20they%20have%20resonated%20with%20women.%20Many%20of%20them%20have%20described%20how%20they%20feel%20to%20see%20other%20women%20vent%20out%20their%20anger%20-%20something%20that%20they%20say%20society%20discourages%20them%20from%20doing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20venting%20out%2C%20some%20unexpected%20emotions%20also%20arise.%20Ms%20Helmus%20said%20instead%20of%20anger%20against%20her%20husband%2C%20she%20felt%20the%20grief%20she'd%20been%20holding%20onto%20since%20witnessing%20the%20death%20of%20a%20friend%20when%20she%20was%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPsychotherapists%2C%20however%2C%20say%20there%20is%20one-size-fits-all%20solution%20to%20deal%20with%20anger.%20Psychotherapist%20Stephanie%20Sarkis%20told%20%3Cem%3EUSA%20Today%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20some%20people%20handle%20rage%20with%20activating%20strategies%2C%20like%20hitting%20a%20punching%20bag%20or%20doing%20an%20intense%20workout.%20For%20others%2C%20soothing%20strategies%2C%20like%20deep%20breaths%2C%20slow%20walks%20or%20calm%20music%2C%20work%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716887760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fr4tloig_woman-in-rage-pexels_625x300_28_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fnew-viral-rage-ritual-trend-has-women-screaming-smashing-sticks-5763242%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Participants%20are%20encouraged%20to%20think%20of%20people%20and%20experiences%20that%20have%20wronged%20them%20and%20to%20scream%20and%20swing%20the%20sticks%20for%20at%20least%2020%20minutes%2C%20or%20until%20they%20can%20no%20longer%20move%20their%20arms.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fnew-viral-rage-ritual-trend-has-women-screaming-smashing-sticks-5763242%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fnew-viral-rage-ritual-trend-has-women-screaming-smashing-sticks-5763242%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fnew-viral-rage-ritual-trend-has-women-screaming-smashing-sticks-5763242%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Some%20wealthy%20people%20trying%20to%20sell%20their%20luxury%20homes%20are%20struggling%22%2C%22con