html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BHardik%20Wasn't%20A%20Free%20Man%2C%20A%20Lot%20Going%20On%26quot%3B%3A%20Harbhajan%20On%20Poor%20IPL%20Show%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20India%20off-spinner%20Harbhajan%20Singh%20has%20nothing%20but%20empathy%20for%20Hardik%20Pandya%20as%20he%20navigates%20a%20challenging%20phase%20in%20his%20career%20and%20is%20hopeful%20that%20the%20all-rounder%2C%20who%20%26quot%3Bhasn't%20been%20a%20free%20man%20in%20the%20last%20two%20months%26quot%3B%2C%20will%20become%20one%20during%20next%20month's%20T20%20World%20Cup.%20Pandya%20endured%20a%20forgettable%20IPL%20both%20as%20captain%20and%20player%20with%20his%20team%20Mumbai%20Indians%20ending%20bottom%20of%20the%20heap%20in%20the%20points%20table.%20What%20made%20things%20worse%20was%20the%20incessant%20jeering%20of%20fans%20whenever%20he%20took%20the%20field%2C%20including%20at%20MI's%20home%20turf%20--%20the%20Wankhede%20Stadium.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Harbhajan%20expects%20the%20tide%20to%20turn%20in%20the%20Americas%20during%20the%20T20%20showpiece.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20he%20wears%20that%20blue%20jersey%2C%20he%20will%20be%20a%20different%20Hardik%20Pandya%20because%20we%20know%20he%20can%20score%20those%20runs%20and%20take%20those%20wickets.%20I%20want%20Hardik%20to%20come%20good%20as%20he%20has%20gone%20through%20a%20lot%20and%20I%20wish%20him%20all%20the%20very%20best%20to%20have%20a%20very%20good%20tournament%20for%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20Harbhajan%20told%20PTI%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20he%20has%20a%20good%20tournament%2C%20obviously%20India%20will%20have%20a%20great%20chance%20to%20go%20forward%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYes%2C%20his%20form%20is%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20concern...and%20lot%20of%20other%20stuff%20was%20going%20on%20around%20him%2C%20his%20shifting%20from%20Gujarat%20to%20Mumbai%2C%20was%20a%20big%20change%20and%20the%20team%20(MI)%20didn't%20react%20too%20well%20to%20Hardik%20coming%20back%20and%20that%20too%20as%20captain%2C%26quot%3B%20the%2043-year-old%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reason%20for%20the%20fan%20backlash%20against%20Pandya%20was%20MI's%20decision%20to%20hand%20him%20the%20captaincy%20after%20taking%20it%20away%20from%20the%20long-serving%20Rohit%20Sharma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20speculation%20throughout%20the%20season%20that%20MI's%20dressing%20room%20was%20a%20divided%20house%20due%20to%20the%20change%20of%20guard.%20Rohit%20will%20now%20captain%20the%20national%20side%20with%20Pandya%20as%20his%20deputy%20in%20the%20World%20Cup%20starting%20June%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarbhajan%2C%20a%20multi%20format%20World%20Cup-winner%2C%20urged%20the%20team%20management%20to%20bring%20Pandya%20and%20Rohit%20on%20%26quot%3Bsame%20page%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...it%20looked%20like%20they%20(MI)%20were%20not%20playing%20together%20as%20a%20team.%20So%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20going%20on.%20Hardik%20wasn't%20a%20free%20man%20in%20the%20last%20two%20months.%20I%20believe%20both%20of%20them%20and%20many%20others%20who%20have%20played%20in%20different%20teams%20will%20have%20to%20come%20together%20to%20do%20something%20special%20for%20the%20nation...%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWinning%20a%20World%20Cup%20is%20a%20bigger%20achievement%20than%20winning%20an%20IPL%20trophy%2C%20so%20I%20would%20urge%20the%20management%20to%20bring%20everyone%20together%2C%20have%20them%20on%20one%20page%20and%20make%20sure%20they%20play%20like%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20believe%20it's%20the%20responsibility%20of%20the%20management%20to%20come%20together%20and%20win%20together.%20Even%20if%20they%20lose%20they%20should%20be%20losing%20together.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBumrah%20will%20need%20support%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJasprit%20Bumrah%20is%20the%20only%20speedster%20among%20the%20chosen%20three%20(the%20other%20two%20being%20Arshdeep%20Singh%20and%20Mohammed%20Siraj)%2C%20who%20doesn't%20need%20conditions%20to%20be%20successful%2C%20feels%20Harbhajan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPace%20attack%20definitely%20could%20be%20a%20concern%20because%20because%20Bumrah%20is%20in%20a%20different%20league%20for%20the%20kind%20of%20bowler%20he%20is.%20He%20will%20win%20you%20games%20on%20any%20kind%20of%20pitch.%20He%20doesn't%20need%20conditions%20whereas%20other%20bowlers%20like%20Arshdeep%20and%20Siraj%20would%20need%20help%20from%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20there's%20bounce%2C%20Siraj%20might%20do%20well.%20He%20is%20tall%2C%20can%20also%20swing%20it%20both%20ways%2C%20hits%20the%20deck%20hard%20and%20has%20got%20pace.%20But%20if%20wickets%20are%20slow%20then%20the%20challenge%20begins%20for%20other%20bowlers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20will%20be%20lot%20of%20responsibility%20on%20Bumrah's%20shoulders%20but%20I%20hope%20other%20guys%20also%20take%20responsibility%20to%20be%20someone%20special.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIPL%20performances%20won't%20matter%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarbhajan%20said%20IPL%20form%20would%20make%20no%20difference%20to%20the%20players'%20fortunes%20in%20the%20ICC%20showpiece.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20matter%20what%20you%20have%20done%20in%20your%20IPL%20career%20or%20previously%2C%20this%20is%20what%20counts%20the%20most...if%20I%20was%20in%20their%20shoes%2C%20I%20would%20be%20looking%20for%20this%20opportunity%20to%20showcase%20that%20I%20have%20been%20better%20than%20what%20I%20have%20been%20doing%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20'Turbanator'%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVirat%20is%20a%20changed%20T20%20batter%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarbhajan%20was%20mighty%20impressed%20with%20how%20Virat%20Kohli%20tweaked%20his%20T20%20game%20during%20this%20year's%20IPL%20by%20adding%20shots%20to%20his%20repertoire%2C%20which%20drastically%20improved%20his%20strike%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVirat%20has%20shown%20a%20lot%20of%20improvement%20from%20last%20year%20to%20this%20year%20and%20people%20spoke%20about%20his%20strike%20rate.%20It%20was%20in%20130s%20during%20last%20year%20and%20this%20time%20it%20is%20in%20160s%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOf%20course%20it's%20a%20big%20big%20change.%20Virat%20and%20Rohit%20will%20have%20to%20score%20quickly%20in%20Powerplay%20but%20also%20need%20to%20respect%20the%20conditions%20in%20USA%20and%20West%20Indies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIf%20Gambhir%20becomes%20coach%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarbhajan%20doesn't%20know%20whether%20Gautam%20Gambhir%2C%20who%20is%20being%20spoken%20of%20as%20the%20favourite%20to%20take%20over%20India's%20head%20coach%20position%20from%20the%20outgoing%20Rahul%20Dravid%2C%20will%20get%20the%20job%20but%20he%20does%20believe%20it%20would%20be%20a%20crown%20of%20thorns%20for%20whoever%20chooses%20to%20wear%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20say%20it%20properly%2C%20it%20is%20a%20speculation%2C%20which%20is%20doing%20rounds...the%20biggest%20thing%20a%20coach%20can%20do%20is%20to%20bring%20everyone%20together%2C%20so%20that%20team%20plays%20together.%20So%2C%20whether%20Gautam%20becomes%20coach%20or%20Ashish%20Nehra%2C%20or%20whosoever%20gets%20the%20opportunity%2C%20hope%20they%20do%20better%20than%20what%20others%20before%20them%20did.%26quot%3B%20He%20also%20ruled%20himself%20out%20of%20the%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20I%20will%20be%20able%20to%20give%20that%20much%20time.%20At%20this%20stage%20of%20my%20life%20I%20have%20a%20young%20family%20and%20I%20need%20to%20be%20around%20them%20and%20look%20after%20them.%20Yes%2C%20when%20the%20right%20time%20comes%2C%20I%20will%20put%20my%20foot%20forward%20and%20say%20I%20am%20ready%20for%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and