the%20election%20for%20Delhi's%20seven%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats.%20He%20was%20released%20till%20June%201%20and%20told%20to%20return%20to%20Tihar%20Jail%20by%20June%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20hopes%20of%20an%20immediate%20hearing%20were%20dashed%20after%20a%20vacation%20bench%20said%20it%20would%20only%20forward%20his%20plea%20to%20Chief%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%2C%20who%20will%20decide%20when%20it%20will%20be%20heard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20CJI%20will%20take%20an%20appropriate%20decision%20on%20listing%20this%20plea%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20of%20Justice%20JK%20Maheshwari%20and%20KV%20Vishwanathan%20said%2C%20noting%20the%20verdict%20in%20the%20original%20case%20-%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20challenging%20his%20arrest%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20-%20had%20been%20reserved%20after%20the%20last%20hearing%20on%20May%2017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20had%20sought%20an%20urgent%20hearing%20for%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejiwal-leaves-jail-after-50-days-election-gamechanger-says-aap-5633876%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKejriwal%20Leaves%20Jail%20After%2050%20Days%2C%20Says%20%26quot%3BNeed%20To%20Fight%20Dictatorship%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20seemed%20a%20little%20put%20out%20by%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20bail%20extension%20plea%2C%20pointing%20out%20it%20could%20have%20been%20made%20last%20week%2C%20when%20Justice%20Dipankar%20Datta%20-%20who%20was%20part%20of%20the%20bench%20that%20granted%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20interim%20bail%20-%20was%20hearing%20cases.%20Why%20did%20you%20not%20mention%20this...%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20now%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20must%20return%20to%20jail%20as%20ordered%20(by%20June%202)%20or%20face%20the%20court's%20wrath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BKejriwal%20Suffers%20Aggressive%20Form%20Of%20Diabetes%26quot%3B%2C%20Court%20Told%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20AAP%20leader%2C%20represented%20by%20senior%20advocate%20Abhishek%20Manu%20Singhvi%2C%20had%20pressed%20for%20an%20immediate%20hearing%20of%20his%20client's%20plea%2C%20arguing%20that%20time%20was%20needed%20for%20more%20medical%20tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20said%20he%20would%20surrender%20on%20June%209%20(five%20days%20after%20the%20election%20results).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20view%20of%20health%20complications%20and%20increased%20risk%20signs%2C%20a%20medical%20examination%20is%20necessary%20to%20protect%20him%20from%20possible%20long-term%20harm%20to%20during%20his%20prison%20term%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singhvi%20stressed%2C%20underlining%20the%20AAP%20leader%20will%20remain%20%26quot%3Bvisible%20and%20available%20in%20public%26quot%3B%20while%20out%20on%20bail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-delhi-liquor-policy-case-arvind-kejriwal-claims-tihar-officials-negligence-took-toll-on-his-health-5761987%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKejriwal%20Claims%20Tihar%20Officials'%20%26quot%3BNegligence%26quot%3B%20Took%20Toll%20On%20His%20Health%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20risk%20of%20fleeing%20the%20legal%20process%20and%20conditions%20set%20by%20Supreme%20Court%20(for%20interim%20bail)%20have%20been%20followed...%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20lawyer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20medical%20examination%20Mr%20Singhvi%20referred%20to%20were%20ordered%20by%20a%20doctor%20from%20a%20private%20hospital%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%20Tests%20ordered%20include%20PET-CT%20scan%20of%20the%20whole%20body.%20These%20tests%20have%20to%20be%20done%20in%20an%20order%20and%20require%20approximately%20five%20to%20seven%20days%20to%20complete%2C%20the%20court%20was%20told.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Tihar%20