for%20his%20father%20who%20is%20a%20''big%20believer%20of%20new%20technology%20and%20clean%20tech.''%20However%2C%20just%20after%20six%20months%2C%20the%20electric%20scooter%20started%20having%20issues.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''Every%20other%20day%20the%20screens%20stopped%20responding%20and%20the%20bike%20needed%20to%20reset.%20It%20takes%205-6%20minutes%20just%20to%20start%20the%20damn%20thing%2C''%20he%20wrote.%20Mr%20Jain%20shared%20how%20the%20service%20care%20executive's%20visit%20also%20didn't%20solve%20anything.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''Now%20the%20scooter%20does%20not%20even%20start%2C%20there%20is%20no%20option%20of%20pickup%20or%20mechanic%20home%20visit%20to%20app.%20The%20service%20centre%20is%20a%20few%20km%20away%2C%20how%20we%20are%20supposed%20to%20bring%20a%20non-functioning%20vehicle%20to%20the%20service%20centre%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere's%20the%20tweet%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EBuying%20this%20piece%20of%20junk%2C%20the%20OLA%20S1%20Pro%2C%20was%20the%20worst%20decision%20ever.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn(A%20thread)%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FOlaElectric%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40OlaElectric%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fola_support%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40ola_support%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FfUwGvJdVJO%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FfUwGvJdVJO%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20RJ%20-%20Rishabh%20Jain%20(%40rishsamjain)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frishsamjain%2Fstatus%2F1794037935463120901%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%2024%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20YouTuber%20claimed%20that%20he%20got%20a%20call%20from%20the%20OLA%20team%20after%20his%20tweet%20went%20viral.%20Soon%20after%2C%20a%20service%20centre%20executive%20visited%20his%20house%20and%20tried%20to%20resolve%20the%20issue%2C%20following%20which%20it%20was%20taken%20to%20a%20workshop.%20They%20even%20provided%20him%20with%20a%20temporary%20scooter%20until%20they%20repaired%20his%20non-functional%20one.%20Mr%20Jain%20finally%20received%20his%20vehicle%20a%20few%20hours%20later%20along%20with%20apologies%20from%20the%20team.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''After%20delivery%2C%20I%20received%20a%20call%20from%20OLA's%20Head%20of%20After%20Sales%20(Jitesh)%20and%20CMO%20(Anshul).%20They%20personally%20apologized%20for%20the%20inconvenience%20my%20father%20faced.%20I%20truly%20appreciate%20the%20concern%20and%20efforts%20shown%20by%20OLA's%20leadership%2C%20even%20at%20odd%20hours.%20%C2%A0I%20hope%20that%20the%201000s%20of%20others%20in%20this%20thread%20who%20have%20issues%20with%20their%20vehicles%20will%20also%20get%20quick%20resolutions.%C2%A0%20I'll%20be%20testing%20the%20scooter%20for%20a%20few%20days%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20the%20issue%20is%20permanently%20resolved%2C''%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tweet%20has%20gone%20viral%2C%20with%20many%20others%20sharing%20similar%20experiences.%20One%20user%20wrote%2C%20''Worst%20decision..%20I%20purchased%20in%20dec%202022%20and%20now%20battery%20didn't%20work%20and%20from%20last%201%20month%20it%20is%20in%20service%20station..%20Too%20much%20bad%20service.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20commented%2C%20''I'm%20also%20facing%20issues%20with%20my%20Ola%20s%201%20pro%20gen%202%2C%20but%20not%20a%20satisfactory%20response%20from%20the%20customer%20service.%20Bad%20build%20quality.%20Worst%20experience%20so%20far%20owning%20a%20ola.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20third%20added%2C%20''I%20want%20Indian%20tech%20to%20succeed%20but%20the%20evidence%20is%20always%20to%20the%20contrary.%20You%20can't%20expect%20great%20tech%20from%20new%20players.''%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716879180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fo5i8i92o_-ola-scoot