20be%20multitudinous%20opinions%20about%20a%20piece%20of%20art.%20To%20reduce%20it%20to%20just%20that%20then%20is%2C%20to%20my%20mind%2C%20a%20disservice%20-%20despite%20my%20having%20no%20doubt%20that%20it's%20a%20stunning%2C%20solid%20film.%20This%20is%20a%20volcano%20that%20has%20finally%20erupted.%20It%20breaks%20open%20hitherto%20closed%20doors%20for%20the%20women%20of%20a%20country%20who%20haven't%20had%20enough%20representation%20in%20international%20cinema%20for%20almost%20forever.%20Against%20that%2C%20Payal%20Kapadia's%20achievement%20is%20like%20a%20Katana%20that%20slices%20through%20the%20stronghold%20of%20the%20past.%20There%20was%20an%20age%20before%20this%2C%20and%20there%20will%20be%20an%20age%20after%20this%20moment.%20There%20will%20be%20-%20hopefully%20-%20no%20going%20back.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENot%20An%20Easy%20World%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeing%20an%20independent%20filmmaker%20myself%2C%20I%20know%20how%20many%20good%20films%20are%20made%20in%20multiple%20languages%20across%20the%20various%20states%20of%20our%20country%20every%20year%2C%20and%20I%20see%20first-hand%20how%20tough%20it%20is%20for%20Indian%20filmmakers%20to%20even%20get%20their%20films%20featured%20at%20festivals%2C%20let%20alone%20get%20selected%2C%20or%2C%20god%20willing%20(I%20say%20this%20as%20an%20atheist)%2C%20win%20anything.%20It%20doesn't%20help%20that%20we%20send%20thousands%20of%20films%20to%20film%20festivals%20abroad%20as%20a%20single%20country%2C%20of%20which%20just%20one%20or%20two%20are%20selected%20to%20represent%20India.%20If%20this%20was%20Singapore%2C%20and%20you%20were%20an%20independent%20filmmaker%20from%20Singapore%2C%20you'd%20be%20one%20amongst%20perhaps%2020%20films%20being%20sent%20abroad%2C%20and%20thus%20you%20would%20have%20a%201%3A20%20chance%20at%20representing%20the%20country.%20%C2%A0Also%2C%20almost%20every%20Indian%20film%20is%20backed%20by%20powerful%20men%20with%20influence%2C%20who%20make%20calls%20and%20send%20emails%20requesting%20for%20the%20film%20to%20be%20considered.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fall-we-imagine-as-light-review-a-genuine-tour-de-force-that-has-nary-a-blemish-4-5-stars-5733041%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0All%20We%20Imagine%20As%20Light%20Review%3A%20A%20Genuine%20Tour%20De%20Force%20That%20Has%20Nary%20A%20Blemish%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20in%20such%20a%20world%20that%20a%20film%20with%20no%20stars%2C%20with%20a%20fairly%20international%20voice%2C%20and%20made%20by%20women%20through%20and%20through%2C%20has%20won%20a%20Cannes%20Grand%20Prix.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20Patronage%20For%20Art%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20some%20perspective%2C%20it's%20difficult%20to%20last%20for%20long%20as%20an%20independent%20filmmaker%20in%20India%2C%20purely%20because%20the%20industry%20is%20self-sustaining%2C%20that%20is%2C%20there%20is%20little%20institutional%20backing.%20To%20an%20outsider%2C%20it%20may%20seem%20easier%20for%20that%20very%20reason%2C%20but%20it's%20not.%20The%20reason%20is%20that%20we%20are%20expected%20to%20not%20just%20make%20films%20with%20no%20institutional%20funding%20or%20support%2C%20but%20any%20independent%20voice%20is%20also%20likely%20to%20diverge%20from%20the%20popular%20cinematic%20template%20and%20tastes%20of%20the%20day.%20And%20so%2C%20chances%20are%20that%20such%20a%20film%20won't%20get%20sold%20because%20it's%20not%20of%20the%20cinematic%20style%20the%20general%20audiences%20are%20used%20to.%20Hence%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20there%20being%20no%20funding%20support%2C%20there%20is%20also%20no%20or%20very%20little%20market%20for%20independent%20films.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Frecap-2023-10-best-indie-films-in-a-year-of-plenty-4768027%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0Recap%202023%3A%2010%20Best%20Indie%20Films%20In%20A%20Year%20Of%20Plenty%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20if%20there%20is%20government%20support%2C%20chances%20are%20that%20criticism%20is%20not%20easy.%20This%20has%20been%20true%20for%20as%20long%20as%20one%20can%20remember%2C%20and%20it%20basically%20means%20that%20the%20film%20will%20have%20to%20be%20apolitical%20-%20or%2C%20of%20a%20favourable%20brand%20of%20politics.%20Which%20then%20means%20that%20its%20characters%20have%20to%20exist%20in%20a%20vacuum%20in%20daily%20life.%20All%20this%20boils%20down%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20in%20spite%20of%20there%20technically%20being%20government%20institutions%20that%20support%20filmmakers%2C%20such%20support%20may%20come%20with%20limitations.%20To%20cite%20a%20personal%20example%2C%20my%20team%20and%20I%20made%20%3Cem%3ENot%20Today%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20film%20about%20suicide%20prevention%20centres%20and%20mental%20health%20that%20took%20us%20two%20years%20to%20complete%2C%20and%20applied%20for%20the%20National%20Award.%20The%20film%20talks%20about%20India's%20underfunded%20and%20barely%20developed%20suicide%20helplines.%20It%20won%20the%20FIPRESCI%20(International%20Federation%20of%20Film%20Critics)%20award%20in%202022%2C%20but%20it's%20yet%20to%20find%20a%20firm%20footing%20in%20India.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20aspect%20is%20film%20schools.%20Independent%20thought%20and%20the%20belief%20that%20cinema%20can%20be%20a%20tool%20for%20social%20change%2C%20that%20cinema%20can%20be%20a%20genuine%20reflection%20of%20a%20society%20with%20no%20rose-tinted%20glass%2C%20is%20built%20into%20people%20at%20film%20schools%20that%20aren't%20about%20commerce.%20Like%20Krzysztof%20Kie%C5%9Blowski%2C%20who%20came%20from%20the%20Lodz%20film%20school%20in%20Poland%2C%20India%2C%20too%2C%20has%20had%20an%20institution%20like%20that%20since%201960%2C%20called%20the%20Film%20and%20Television%20Institute%20of%20India%20(FTII)%2C%20from%20where%20many%20an%20independent%20and%20genuine%20voice%20has%20emerged.%20I%20myself%20am%20a%202004%20graduate%20from%20FTII.%20We%20learnt%20to%20experiment%20there%2C%20we%20learnt%20to%20see%20cinema%20as%20much%20more%20than%20commerce%2C%20and%20we%20worked%20at%20developing%20a%20voice%20that%20is%20deeply%20Indian%20but%20also%20not%20bogged%20down%20necessarily%20by%20the%20commercial%20force-fit%20of%20what%20we%20call%20'Bollywood'.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Film%20Is%20A%20PoV%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20late%20though%2C%20the%20FTII%20has%20been%20under%20fire%20for%20various%20reasons.%20Payal%20Kapadia%20herself%20faces%20a%20legal%20case%20for%20participating%20in%20a%20strike%20against%20the%20dean.%20For%20independent%20voices%20in%20India%2C%20the%20hurdles%20are%20many%3A%20commerce%2C%20lack%20of%20institutionalised%20finance%2C%20and%20sometimes%2C%20curbs%20on%20ideas.%20Kapadia's%20case%20proves%20beyond%20a%20doubt%20that%20filmmakers%20from%20India%20have%20the%20talent%20needed%20to%20take%20cinema%20to%20world%20platforms%20and%20win%20big.%20Why%20don't%20we%20have%20enough%20support%20within%20the%20boundaries%20of%20the%20country%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20filmmaker%2C%20I%20can%20only%20hope%20that%20Kapadia's%20victory%20as%20a%20filmmaker%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fanasuya-sengupta-on-becoming-first-indian-to-win-best-actress-award-at-cannes-couldn-t-believe-it-5747703%5C%22%3EAnasuya%20Sengupta's%20feat%20as%20the%20first%20Indian%20to%20win%20the%20Cannes%20Best%20Actress%20award%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20push%20the%20institutions%20in%20our%20country%2C%20and%20maybe%20even%20industry%20leaders%2C%20to%20help%20set%20up%20independent%20bodies%20that%20support%20cinema%20as%20a%20pure%20art%20form.%20Without%20patronage%2C%20art%20can%20never%20reach%20the%20brilliance%20it%20has%20the%20potential%20for.%20With%20support%2C%20independent%20cinema%20can%20exist%20independently%2C%20without%20the%20bounds%20or%20perils%20of%20the%20'box%20office'.%20Such%20support%20though%20should%20also%20let%20films%20serve%20as%20a%20mirror%20to%20society.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20more%20grants%20ought%20to%20be%20awarded%20to%20institutes%20like%20the%20FTII%20so%20that%20more%20filmmakers%20from%20smaller%20towns%2C%20cities%20and%20villages%20can%20start%20to%20talk%20about%20the%20India%20they%20see.%20It's%20a%20film.%20It's%20a%20PoV.%20In%20a%20country%20like%20India%2C%20there%20can%20never%20be%20a%20dearth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Aditya%20Kripalani%20is%20an%20independent%20filmmaker%20from%20FTII%2C%20whose%20films%20normally%20talk%20about%20social%20issues.%20His%20works%20include%20'Tikli%20and%20Laxmi%20Bomb'%2C%20'Tottaa%20Pataaka%20Item%20Maal'%2C%20and%20'Not%20Today'.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20views%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716878220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fjfc7t1fg_all-we-imagine-as-light_625x300_26_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fblog%2Flet-this-not-be-only-about-all-we-imagine-as-light-5761895%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Payal%20Kapadia's%20All%20We%20Imagine%20As%20Light%20breaks%20open%20hitherto%20closed%20doors%20for%20the%20women%20of%20a%20country%20who%20haven't%20had%20enough%20representation%20in%20international%20cinema%20for%20almost%20forever.%20Like%20a%20Katana%20sword%2C%20it%20slices%20through%20the%20stronghold%20of%20the%20past.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fblog%2Flet-this-not-be-only-about-all-we-imagine-as-light-5761895%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israel%20continues%20Rafah%20strikes%20after%20dozens%20killed%20in%20Sunday%20bombing%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716878187000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.files.bbci.co.uk%2Fm