%3Fs%3D46%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERed%20Shirt-Shaw%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20she%20%26quot%3Bmade%20the%20difficult%20decision%26quot%3B%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20warnings%2C%20removing%20her%20tribal%20affiliation%20and%20gender%20pronouns%20from%20her%20email%20signature%2C%20%26quot%3Bso%20I%20would%20not%20miss%20the%20remainder%20of%20the%20academic%20year.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20Red%20Shirt-Shaw%20found%20a%20workaround%3A%20She%20has%20continued%20to%20place%20those%20details%20%26quot%3Bin%20the%20body%20of%20each%20email%20that%20I%20send%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20she%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmredshirtshaw%2Fstatus%2F1785366469250879688%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eon%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3Bwill%20not%20be%20challenged%20(for%20now).%26quot%3B%20Little%20has%20done%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Red%20Shirt-Shaw%2C%20including%20those%20details%20is%20personal.%20As%20director%20of%20Native%20Student%20Services%20at%20the%20university%2C%20she%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20feel%20I%20have%20an%20ethical%20responsibility%20to%20claim%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnative-tribes-sue-meta-google-tiktok-teen-social-media-addiction-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etribal%20nations%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20make%20me%20who%20I%20am.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20American%20Civil%20Liberties%20Union's%20South%20Dakota%20chapter%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FACLUSouthDakota%2Fstatus%2F1793668610935910891%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealso%20weighed%20in%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20X.%20The%20group%20called%20the%20Board%20of%20Regents'%20policy%20an%20effort%20by%20the%20state's%20leadership%20%26quot%3Bto%20shove%20queer%20identities%20out%20of%20public%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20experts%20agree%20that%20the%20South%20Dakota%20Board%20of%20Regents'%20guidelines%20are%20an%20escalation%20of%20a%20larger%20movement%20sweeping%20the%20US.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2250e8f9fb-36b8-430f-a575-c8ff593977c5%5C%22%3ELarger%20efforts%20at%20play%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESouth%20Dakota's%20flashpoint%20over%20email%20signatures%20comes%20as%20a%20national%20discourse%20rages%20about%20rights%20for%20LGBTQ%2B%20Americans%20and%20members%20of%20diverse%20and%20protected%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BQuite%20frankly%2C%20this%20is%20the%20first%20time%20I've%20heard%20of%20a%20state%20university%20choosing%20to%20use%20branding%20standards%20to%20eliminate%20what%20obviously%20has%20become%20a%20practice%20of%20including%20pronouns%20and%20tribal%20affiliations%20to%20emails%2C%26quot%3B%20Paulette%20Grandberry%20Russell%2C%20president%20of%20the%20National%20Association%20of%20Diversity%20Officers%20in%20Higher%20Education%2C%20told%20the%20AP.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20I'm%20not%20surprised%2C%20given%20the%20current%20climate%20we're%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added%2C%20calling%20the%20decision%20by%20the%20state's%20Board%20of%20Regents%20a%20%26quot%3Bsteady%20progression%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20broader%20push.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGrandberry%20Russell%20told%20the%20AP%20she%20thinks%20that%20such%20early-stage%20measures%20in%20conservative%20states%20could%20be%20used%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Btesting%20ground%26quot%3B%20to%20determine%20if%20more%20severe%20laws%20could%20take%20hold.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKelly%20Benjamin%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20American%20Association%20of%20University%20Professors%2C%20an%20advocacy%20group%20for%20academics%20in%20higher%20education%2C%20told%20the%20AP%20that%20it's%20the%20latest%20step%20in%20%26quot%3Ba%20longer-term%20agenda%26quot%3B%20aimed%20at%20limiting%20diversity%2C%20equity%2C%20and%20inclusion%20measures%20to%20protect%20LGBTQ%2B%20Americans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBenjamin%20pointed%20to%20recent%20efforts%20in%20states%20like%20Florida%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Farkansas-title-ix-transgender-hu