nts%20possessing%20higher%20incomes%20%E2%80%94%20coupled%20with%20the%20demand%20for%20housing%20%E2%80%94%20home%20prices%20have%20gone%20through%20the%20roof%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F05%2F26%2Fus%2Fpolitics%2Fmontana-senate-bozeman-growth.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20median%20home%20price%20in%20Montana%20hit%20%24425%2C000%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20late%202023%2C%20a%2075%25%20increase%20from%202018%2C%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Bozeman%2C%20which%20has%20become%20a%20hot%20spot%20for%20affluent%20transplants%2C%20the%20median%20home%20price%20has%20risen%20to%20an%20astonishing%20%24770%2C000%2C%20according%20to%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdata.census.gov%2Fall%3Fq%3DBozeman%2520city%2C%2520Montana%2520Populations%2520and%2520People%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20Census%20Bureau%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Bozeman's%20population%20jumped%20from%20roughly%2037%2C000%20to%20more%20than%2053%2C000%20from%202010%20to%202020.%20In%202022%2C%20the%20city's%20population%20grew%20even%20further%20to%2056%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rising%20prices%20have%20shined%20a%20brighter%20light%20on%20housing%20affordability%2C%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-supporting-republican-montana-governor-yimby-housing-policies-lowering-rent-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emany%20native%20Montanans%20have%20been%20priced%20out%20by%20ever-increasing%20rents%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Outside%20of%20Bozeman%2C%20some%20longtime%20residents%20are%20now%20residing%20in%20RVs%20due%20to%20the%20heightened%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20strong%20support%20from%20GOP%20Gov.%20Greg%20Gianforte%2C%20the%20Montana%20legislature%20passed%20housing%20and%20land-use%20reform%20bills%20that%20overhauled%20the%20construction%20process%20%E2%80%94%20and%20now%20permit%20more%20housi