seeds%20in%20the%20refrigerator%20at%20a%20constant%20temperature.%20Do%20not%20deep%20freeze%20them.%20You%20can%20also%20store%20them%20in%20a%20%3Cem%3Ematka%3C%2Fem%3E%20(earthen%20pot)%20as%20well.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAdd%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F348771%2Fgrow-organic-food-doctor-naveen-kumar-farming-workshop-chennai-vegetables-fruits-at-home-gardening%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echarcoal%20powder%20%3C%2Fa%3Einside%20the%20container%20to%20protect%20seeds%20from%20insect%20attacks.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EYou%20can%20store%20seeds%20for%20a%20year.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20particular%20age%20till%20the%20seeds%20are%20fertile%2C%20similar%20to%20human%20beings.%20After%20a%20year%2C%20its%20gene%20will%20become%20weak%20and%20lead%20to%20low%20fruiting%20or%20no%20plant%20growth%20at%20all%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20the%20case%20of%20watermelon%20and%20muskmelon%2C%20sow%20the%20stored%20seeds%20in%20the%20first%20week%20of%20December%20to%20get%20fruits%20in%20March.%20Sow%20other%20summer%20crops%20like%20%3Cem%3Ekakdi%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20winter.%20Vegetables%20like%20%3Cem%3Ekarela%20%3C%2Fem%3Ecan%20be%20harvested%20during%20May%20and%20sown%2045%20days%20prior%20to%20monsoon%20to%20get%20fruiting.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat.%20All%20photos%3A%20Anupama%20Desai.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716618600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FAnupama-Desai-1-1716297393.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D350660%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22For%20the%20past%2014%20years%2C%20Anupama%20Desai%20has%20been%20growing%20seasonal%20vegetables%20and%20collecting%20seeds%20of%20the%20produce%20grown%20at%20home.%20She%20shares%2010%20easy%20tips%20to%20store%20seeds%20in%20summer%20to%20be%20able%20to%20sow%20