ferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F199843%2Fandhra-vet-risks-life-to-save-300-wild-animals-shows-true-humanity%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eveterinary%20clinics%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20owing%20to%20the%20system%E2%80%99s%20apathy%2C%20farmers%20continue%20losing%20their%20only%20assets%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20address%20this%2C%20he%20launched%20%E2%80%98Verdant%20Impact%E2%80%99%20in%202020%20to%20offer%20holistic%20services%20%E2%80%94%20including%20telemedicine%20facilities%2C%20animal%20ICU%2C%20remote%20monitoring%2C%20cattle%20commerce%2C%20and%20virtual%20veterinary%20consultations%20for%20livestock%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOne-stop%20solution%20for%20cattle%20care%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOriginally%20from%20Banswara%2C%20Manish%20dropped%20out%20of%20his%20first%20year%20of%20PhD%20to%20focus%20on%20livestock%20healthcare.%20Talking%20about%20the%20issues%20in%20the%20field%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CUnlike%20cats%20and%20dogs%2C%20the%20biggest%20issue%20is%20that%20farmers%20cannot%20carry%20them%20to%20hospitals%20as%20transportation%20costs%20are%20high%20and%20the%20process%20is%20inconvenient.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FManish-Prahlad-1-1716381157.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Livestock%20plays%20a%20key%20role%20and%20the%20sector%20contributes%20about%206.20%20percent%20of%20the%20total%20GDP%2C%20and%20yet%20their%20healthcare%20remains%20ignored.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FManish-Prahlad-1-1716381157.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FManish-Prahlad-1-1716381157-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F