%20hero%20ingredient%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Ganesh%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20the%20homestay%20boasts%20five%20rooms%2C%20with%20one%20of%20them%20being%20an%20authentic%20mud%20room.%20While%20guests%20are%20on%20the%20farm%2C%20there%20is%20plenty%20to%20keep%20them%20busy%2C%20Ganesh%20says.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20people%20come%20in%20summer%2C%20we%20teach%20them%20how%20to%20identify%20ripe%20mangoes%2C%20climb%20trees%2C%20pluck%20mangoes%20and%20then%20ripen%20them%2C%20and%20prepare%3Cem%3E%20chutneys%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20juice.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%20that%20in%20the%20monsoons%2C%20guests%20are%20treated%20to%20lessons%20in%20paddy%20cultivation.%20%E2%80%9CI%20take%20them%20on%20tractor%20rides%2C%20let%20them%20drive%20the%20tractors%2C%20and%20show%20them%20our%20organic%20harvesting%20methods.%E2%80%9D%20When%20farming%20isn%E2%80%99t%20keeping%20guests%20occupied%2C%20Ganesh%20takes%20them%20boating%20and%20bird%20watching%2C%20and%20also%20lets%20them%20in%20on%20some%20mango%20canning%20secrets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeedless%20to%20say%2C%20mango%20features%20in%20almost%20every%20dish%20at%20the%20homestay%2C%20sometimes%20as%20a%20side%20dish%2C%20other%20times%20as%20the%20hero%20ingredient.%20%3Cem%3EAamti%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20spicy%2C%20sweet%20and%20sour%20%3Cem%3Edal%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20pickles%2C%20%3Cem%3Epanna%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20cooling%20Indian%20summer%20drink%20made%20with%20unripe%20green%20mangoes)%2C%20%3Cem%3Echutneys%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Eaamras%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20milky%20drink%20made%20with%20mango%20pulp)%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F336600%2Ftech-nursery-hydroponics-aeroponics-farming-ratlam-brothers-arbind-ravindra-dhakad%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efresh%20fruit%20%3C%2Fa%3Eare%20some%20of%20the%20delights%20offered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20Ganesh%2C%20he%20maintains%20that%2