.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20a%20time%20when%20people%20are%20bothered%20by%20soaring%20prices%20of%20cow%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F173064%2Fmilk-cow-camel-almond-coconut-yak-goat-soy-coconut-alternative-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuffaloes%20milk%20%3C%2Fa%3Eat%20Rs%2060%20per%20litre%2C%20they%20are%20not%20interested%20in%20buying%20donkey%20milk%20which%20is%20sold%20for%20Rs%203%2C500%20a%20litre.%20But%20it%20has%20an%20international%20market%20and%20is%20widely%20used%20in%20pharmaceutical%20and%20cosmetics%20industries%20to%20make%20products%20like%20moisturisers%2C%20baby%20cream%2C%20and%20soaps%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC7555024%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2020%20research%20article%20%3C%2Fa%3Ereveals%20that%20donkey%20milk%20stimulates%20the%20immune%20system%2C%20regulates%20the%20gastrointestinal%20flora%2C%20and%20prevents%20inflammatory%20diseases.%20It%20has%20long%20been%20used%20as%20an%20alternative%20for%20infants%20and%20patients%20with%20Cow%E2%80%99s%20Milk%20Protein%20Allergy%20(CMPA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fdonkey-milk-1-1716196416.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%202022%2C%20Dhiren%20started%20TDS%20Donkey%20Farm%20without%20any%20formal%20training.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fdonkey-milk-1-1716196416.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fdonkey-milk-1-1716196416-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2