y%20and%20bought%20their%20annual%20package%20of%20Rs%203.5%20lakh%20which%20brought%20in%20customers.%20After%20more%20than%20a%20year%2C%20I%20got%20my%20first%20order%20of%2050%20kg%20milk%20powder%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20that%20time%2C%20Dhiren%20had%20already%20stored%20200%20kg%20of%20milk%20powder.%20He%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20takes%2017%20litres%20of%20milk%20to%20make%20one%20kg%20powder.%20It%20is%20sold%20for%20Rs%2063%2C000%20per%20kg%20in%20the%20international%20market%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20initial%20hiccups%2C%20Dhiren%20was%20able%20to%20scale%20up%20the%20business%20and%20gradually%20expanded%20his%20farm%20to%2050%20donkeys.%20The%20current%20daily%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F255951%2Fhyderabad-sids-farm-iit-kharagpur-cow-cattle-earns-crores-milk-subscription-plan-dairy-revenue-kishore-indukuri-inspirational-success-vid01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emilk%20production%20%3C%2Fa%3Eat%20his%20farm%20is%20about%2015%20litres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%20that%20he%20also%20ensures%20the%20general%20well-being%20of%20the%20donkeys%20at%20his%20farm.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20make%20sure%20that%20the%20donkeys%20are%20not%20exploited%20for%20milk.%20In%20our%20village%2C%20we%20have%20a%20veterinary%20hospital%20very%20close%20to%20our%20farm.%20We%20get%20them%20treated%20and%20vaccinated%20for%20tetanus%20every%20year%20and%20give%20them%20B-complex%20supplements%20every%20month%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%20at%20his%20success%2C%20Dhiren%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWith%20this%20work%2C%20I%20feel%20I%20have%20also%20been%20able%20to%20raise%20some%20respect%20for%20donkeys%20that%20are%20considered%20of%20no%20value%20in%20the%20Indian%20setup.%20Besides%2C%20I%20have%20also%20been%20able%20to%20get%20fame%20at%20a%20very%20young%20age.%20Had%20I%20been%20in%20a%20government%20job%2C%20n