explain%20why%20this%20is%20a%20miracle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20a%20time%20when%20even%20two%20bicycles%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20pass%20simultaneously.%20What%20else%20can%20you%20expect%20from%20a%20two-foot-wide%20road%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asks.%20I%20agree.%20So%2C%20naturally%2C%20watching%20the%20path%20accommodating%20trucks%20and%20lorries%20is%20amusing%20for%20the%20villagers.%20The%20farmer%20is%20quick%20to%20hail%20his%20ex-%3Cem%3Esarpanch%20%3C%2Fem%3E(a%20decision-maker%20elected%20by%20the%20village)%20Chhavi%20Rajawat%20for%20this%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F85603%2Fwomen-sarpanches-transforming-inspiring-villages%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ephenomenal%20work%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20stresses%20though%20that%20this%20isn%E2%80%99t%20the%20only%20transformation%20she%20has%20brought%20about.%20%E2%80%9COur%20village%20has%20water%20thanks%20to%20her.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20Rajawat%20took%20over%20as%20%3Cem%3Esarpanch%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%202010%20%E2%80%94%20at%20the%20time%20making%20headlines%20for%20being%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20%3Cem%3Esarpanch%3C%2Fem%3E%20with%20an%20MBA%20degree%20%E2%80%94%20the%20village%20was%20experiencing%20one%20of%20its%20worst%20droughts.%20%E2%80%9CMadam%20ensured%20a%20pipeline%20in%20every%20house%20and%20water%20in%20every%20pond%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ladu%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHome%20isn%E2%80%99t%20the%20only%20place%20where%20he%20has%20been%20witnessing%20the%20results%20of%20Rajawat%E2%80%99s%20work.%20His%20fields%20too%20have%20benefited.%20Promising%20to%20send%20me%20pictures%20of%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F313207%2Faravinthan-coimbatore-organic-farm-seed-bank-preserves-rare-varieties-vegetables-pulses%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethriving%20pulses%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20farmer%20credits%20the%20steady%20supply%20of%20water%20for%20this.%20%E2%80%9CEarlier%20my%20fields%20would%20dry%20up%20completely.%20But%20not%20anymore.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20suffices%20to%20say%20that%20in%20the%20two%20terms%20that%20Rajawat%20headed%20the%20village%20as%20%3Cem%3Esarpanch%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%202010-15%20and%202015-20%2C%20she%20shaped%2C%20both%2C%20policies%20and%20dreams.%20As%20she%20points%20out%2C%20the%20victory%20is%20personal.%20After%20all%2C%20this%20is%20her%20native%20village.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20she%20was%20chasing%20corporate%20dreams%20%E2%80%94%20Rajawat%20worked%20for%20a%20slew%20of%20multinational%20companies%20after%20completing%20her%20MBA%20degree%20%E2%80%94%20one%20question%20continued%20to%20baffle%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20government%20funding%20for%20rural%20development%20increasing%20over%20the%20years%2C%20why%20were%20villages%20not%20progressing%3F%20Why%20was%20development%20in%20retreat%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConversations%20with%20the%20villagers%20led%20her%20to%20the%20answer.%20%E2%80%9CI%20began%20to%20understand%20that%20responsibility%20and%20ownership%20were%20slowly%20regressing%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fsearch%3Fq%3Dindian%2Bvillages%2Bthe%2Bbetter%2Bindia%26rlz%3D1C1YTUH_enIN1048IN1048%26oq%3Dindian%2Bvillages%2Bthe%2Bbetter%2Bindia%26gs_lcrp%3DEgZjaHJvbWUyBggAEEUYOTIJCAEQIRgKGKABMgkIAhAhGAoYoAHSAQg0OTcyajBqNKgCALACAA%26sourceid%3Dchrome%26ie%3DUTF-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erural%20landscapes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20469px)%20100vw%2C%20469px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSarpanch-Chhavi-with-the-goat_11zon-1715862357.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22469%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ex-Sarpanch%20Chhavi%20Rajawat%20h